                <aside class="iititle"><span><i class="icon-user icon-large"></i> <a href="http://www.taotsang.com/author/admin" title="由道藏网发布" rel="author">道藏网</a></span><span><i class="icon-folder-open icon-large"></i> <a href="http://www.taotsang.com/a/dianji" rel="category tag">典籍</a></span><span><i class="icon-eye-open icon-large"></i> 围观296次</span><span><i class="icon-comment-alt icon-large"></i> <a href="http://www.taotsang.com/509.html#respond" class="ds-thread-count" data-thread-key="509">留下评论</a></span></aside>
